            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://dthtfcuddles.github.io/comic/001/</guid>
            <category type="storyline">Chapter 1: The Gig</category>
            <category type="character">Sher</category>
            <category type="character">Rowi</category>
            <category type="character">Daniel</category>
            <category type="tag">Space Station</category>
            <category type="tag">Show</category>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://dthtfcuddles.github.io/your_content/comics/001/Page_1.png" alt_text="A band playing at a space station, nothing unusual here"></p>

<hr>

<p>The idea that sparked this comic had been in development for a while, along with a lot of world building.<br />
However, the comic itself was started randomly in an inspiration moment, and finished in record time between commissions.</p>

<p>I will talk about things like how this comic returned me the motivation and love I had for drawing comics once I post the last page of this chapter. But right now, enjoy this comic.</p>

<p>This is not going to be a fetish comic. Its actually marked as a 15+ comic due to swearing and touching some dark topics- stuff that comes with the territory when we're talking about rock and metal music.</p>
]]></description>
